author: Cindy Sui
title: Taiwan's coronavirus success bolsters case for joining WHO, experts say
description: A dispute over whether Taiwan warned of human-to-human transmission of the coronavirus before China did has renewed calls to allow the island to join the World Health Organization.
content:
TAIPEI, Taiwan A dispute over whether Taiwan warned the World Health Organization about human-to-human transmission of the coronavirus before China did has renewed calls to allow the island to join the organization, over the strong objections of Beijing.
